  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, sauté onion and carrot over medium heat until soft.",
    "Add potato, celery root, and mushrooms; cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and white wine (if using), bring to a boil.",
    "Add thyme and bay leaf (if using), then reduce heat to low.",
    "Simmer covered for 30 minutes until vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in almond milk and cook gently for 5 minutes to thicken.",
    "Remove bay leaf and serve hot."
  ],
